{"type": "doc", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "El objetivo fundamental de un sistema de comunicaciones, es", "type": "text"}, {"text": " ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": "#9B9B9B", "backgroundColor": null}}]}, {"text": "transferir informaci\u00f3n de un lugar a otro", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": "#9B9B9B", "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}, {"type": "highlight", "attrs": {"color": null}}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "3 PARCIALES\u2192 1 TEORIA, 2 PRACTICA", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Comunicacion desde el punto de vista tecnico", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Transmitir resivir y procesar informaci\u00f3n que se quiere procezar", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Toda nuestra info se transforma en se\u00f1ales que se expresan en ondas", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": " Existen 2 tipode de funte de  infotmaci\u00f3n", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "\u00b0 Forma anal\u00f3gica (continua) ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 2, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Dos ejemplos serian la musica y voz humana", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 2, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Tiene variacion continua en el tiempo", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-m70hd4gvzkc-1773615740138.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "\u00b0 Fomra digital (discreta) ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 2, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Un ejemplo son los numero expresados en binario", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 2, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Onda digital tiene varicacion discontinua en el tiempo", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-yfd9xcroj2-1773615740587.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Al principio todos querian transportar la voz\u2192 surge la radio", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "\u201cSamuel Morse desarroll\u00f3 en 1837 el primer sistema electr\u00f3nico de comunicaciones.", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Us\u00f3 la inducci\u00f3n electromagn\u00e9tica para", "type": "text"}, {"text": " transferir informaci\u00f3n en forma de puntos, rayas y espacios entre un transmisor y un receptor sencillos, ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": "usando una l\u00ednea de transmisi\u00f3n que consist\u00eda en un tramo de conductor met\u00e1lico. Llam\u00f3 tel\u00e9grafo a su invento.\u201c", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Antes al comunicarse 2 personas era con ayuda de un intermediario, que conectaba a 2 personas, se remplazo a esa persona gracias a una central electronica,", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " al aparecer los sistemas digitales se digitalizaron todas las centrales y desaparecieron las operadoras (las intermediarias)", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Mdios de transmision divisi\u00f3n en grupos", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "No guiados:", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Coneexion a conexion inalambrica, wifi, bluetooth", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Guiados: ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "calbes, fibra optica, etc", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "details", "attrs": {"open": true}, "content": [{"type": "detailsSummary", "attrs": {"level": 1}, "content": [{"text": "Marconi pionero en la creaci\u00f3n de las radios", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "detailsContent", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Creador de la radio (AM\u2192 amplitud modulada)", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "details", "attrs": {"open": true}, "content": [{"type": "detailsSummary", "attrs": {"level": 1}, "content": [{"text": "Edwin Howard", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "detailsContent", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Creador radio (FM\u2192 modulacion de frecuencia)", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "No guiados:", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Coneexion a conexion inalambrica, wifi, bluetooth Guiados: calbes, fibra optica, etc", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Esquema Sistemas de Comunicaciones (diagrama simplificado)", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "ANTES DEL TRANSMISOR viene un modulador", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-gadch39izzd-1773615741124.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Fuente info: personas que van a hablar", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Transmisor: transmite al medio de transmision\u2192guiado/ no guiado", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Receptor: Quien interpreta la se\u00f1al emitida", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Destino de informacion: Persona que escucha el msj", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Ancho de banda espectral\u2192 frecuencia max - frecuencia min", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "longitud onda periodo q recorre en una se\u00f1al senoidal", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Tipos de Sistemas de Comunicaciones", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Es aquel en el cual la ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "energ\u00eda se transmite y se recibe en forma anal\u00f3gica, una se\u00f1al de variaci\u00f3n continua, como por ejemplo una onda senoidal", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Lo podemos ver por la funci\u00f3n\u2192 v(t)= A.sen ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": null}}]}, {"text": "(2", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\pi"}}, {"text": "f.t+", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\theta"}}, {"text": ")", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/ez3hr96fn2v-1773773624216.png", "align": "left", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\omega"}}, {"text": "=2 f \u2192frecuencia angular ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": " A= aplitud ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": " t= tiempo ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": " V(t)= Voltaje ", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\theta"}}, {"text": "=Fase", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Ancho de banda (B)", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": " Es el ", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\Delta"}}, {"text": " entre f max y f min", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/rd4ykmz1xsb-1773773975835.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "ecuaci\u00f3n de dispersi\u00f3n\u00a0o\u00a0relaci\u00f3n de dispersi\u00f3n de onda", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}, {"type": "highlight", "attrs": {"color": "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)"}}]}, {"text": ", expresada como\u00a0:", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": "rgb(10, 10, 10)", "backgroundColor": "rgb(255, 255, 255)"}}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 6, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "C= f.", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\lambda"}}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 6, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Donde C es el a velocidad de la luz / 10^8", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 6, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "f la frecuencia", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 6, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\lambda"}}, {"text": " la longitud de onda", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 4, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Podemo deducir gracias a esto que:", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}, {"text": "Mientras mayor sea la f menor sera la longitud de onda y viceberza", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 2, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Modulaci\u00f3n y Demodulaci\u00f3n", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "La modulaci\u00f3n se hace en un transmisor mediante un circuito llamado ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "modulador", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": ".", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Una portadora sobre la que ha actuado una se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "se llama onda modulada o se\u00f1al modulada. ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " fc", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": null}}]}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "La demodulaci\u00f3n es el proceso inverso a la modulaci\u00f3n, y ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "reconvierte a la portadora modulada en la informaci\u00f3n original ", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": "(es decir, quita la informaci\u00f3n de la portadora). La demodulaci\u00f3n se hace en un receptor, con un circuito llamado ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "demodulador.", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Tipos de Modulaci\u00f3n", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n es anal\u00f3gica, y la amplitud (V) de la portadora es proporcional a ella, se produce la modulaci\u00f3n de Amplitud (AM, por amplitude modulation).", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si se var\u00eda la frecuencia (f ) en forma proporcional a la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n, se produce la modulaci\u00f3n de frecuencia (FM, de frequency modulaion).", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Finalmente si se var\u00eda la fase (\ud835\udf03) en proporci\u00f3n con la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n, se produce la modulaci\u00f3n de fase (PM, de phase modulation)", "type": "text"}]}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 3, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Tipos de Modulacion", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "bulletList", "content": [{"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n es digital, y la amplitud (V) de la portadora se var\u00eda proporcionalmente a la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n, se produce una se\u00f1al modulada digitalmente, llamada ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "modulaci\u00f3n por conmutaci\u00f3n de amplitud", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " (ASK, de amplitude shift keying).", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si la frecuencia (f ) var\u00eda en forma proporcional a la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n digital se produce la ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "modulaci\u00f3n por conmutaci\u00f3n de frecuencia", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " (FSK, de frequency shift keying).", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si la fase ( ", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\theta"}}, {"text": ") var\u00eda de manera proporcional a la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n digital, se produce la ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "modulaci\u00f3n por conmutaci\u00f3n de fase", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " (PSK, de phase shift keying).", "type": "text"}]}]}, {"type": "listItem", "content": [{"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Si se var\u00edan al mismo tiempo la amplitud y la fase en proporci\u00f3n con la se\u00f1al de informaci\u00f3n, resulta la ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "modulaci\u00f3n de amplitud en cuadratura", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "textStyle", "attrs": {"color": null, "backgroundColor": "#881337"}}]}, {"text": " (QAM, de quadrature amplitude modulation)", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/lmq39glfgn-1773774836027.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "77.64550264550265%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}]}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Modulacion digital vs analogica", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Digital:", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/bsxmhx2mah-1773775273656.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Analogica:", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/vae49oa1ni-1773775257807.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "antena direccional (", "type": "text"}, {"type": "math", "attrs": {"formula": "\\lambda"}}, {"text": "/4)", "type": "text"}, {"type": "hardBreak"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-a4348lfync8-1773615741794.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-5ahdvc8jwjp-1773615742270.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "antena omnidireccional", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "transmite y reciben campos electromacneticos al igual q la direccional", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-fahqi7nii7t-1773615742866.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Para una comunicacion de calidad debe haber distintas frecuencias de caso contrario hay interferencia, no combiene transmitir en su frecuencia natural", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "Modulador", "type": "text"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": "left"}, "content": [{"text": "Varia amplitud, frecuencia, fase ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "DE UNA ONDA", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}, {"type": "highlight", "attrs": {"color": null}}]}]}, {"type": "image", "attrs": {"alt": null, "src": "https://ndmjrcinfugswtlknebl.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/notion-images/migration-1df7e045-422f-4042-96dc-0b74de6e070d-kiuo5qxf79-1773615743759.png", "align": "center", "title": null, "width": "100%", "position": {"x": 0, "y": 0}, "isFloating": false}}, {"type": "paragraph", "attrs": {"indent": 0, "textAlign": null}}, {"type": "heading", "attrs": {"level": 1, "indent": 0, "textAlign": null}, "content": [{"text": "El ancho de banda es la ", "type": "text"}, {"text": "capacidad m\u00e1xima de datos que una conexi\u00f3n de red puede transmitir simult\u00e1neamente en un tiempo determinado", "type": "text", "marks": [{"type": "bold"}, {"type": "highlight", "attrs": {"color": "rgba(